Inspect lifecycle-bearing network work

Usage:
  agh network work [command]

Available Commands:
  lookup      Show one network work item
  status      Show one network work item

Flags:
  -h, --help   help for work

Global Flags:
      --json            Emit JSON output
  -o, --output string   Output format: human, json, jsonl, or toon (default "human")

Use "agh network work [command] --help" for more information about a command.
